Trinity AI Safeguards

```python
class TrinitySafetyProtocols:
    def __init__(self):
        self.ethical_constraints = HardcodedValues()
        self.human_oversight = RequiredApproval()
        self.fail_safe = AutomaticShutdown()
    
    def ensure_safe_operation(self):
        # Continuous ethical monitoring
        if not self.ethical_constraints.satisfied():
            self.fail_safe.activate()
        
        # Human-in-the-loop for major decisions
        if decision.impact_level > threshold:
            return await self.human_oversight.get_approval()
```

